                    </a>

                    <p>I guess someone had the idea when they saw how many were lying around the city being used as supports for buildings in the red zone...</p>

                    <a href="images/posts/christchurch-new-zealand/christchurch-15_8487658381_o-large.jpg" class="fancybox">
                        <img src="images/posts/christchurch-new-zealand/christchurch-15_8487658381_o.jpg"/>
